---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import headshot from "../assets/headshot.jpg";
import GitHub from "../components/socials/GitHub.astro";
import LinkedIn from "../components/socials/LinkedIn.astro";
import Email from "../components/socials/Email.astro";
import HighlightsCard from "../components/HighlightsCard.astro";
---

<Layout title="Daniel Pan">
	<div class="page">
		<div class="bio">
			<div class="bio-headshot">
				<Image
					src={headshot}
					alt="Headshot of Daniel"
					class="bio-headshot--image"
				/>
			</div>
			<div class="content">
				<header>
					<h1 class="hero_title">
						Hi, I'm
						<br />
						<span class="hero_title--name">Daniel</span> ðŸ‘‹
					</h1>
				</header>
				<main>
					<p>
						I'm a <span class="text-primary">Computer Science</span>
						student at University of British Columbia. I love making projects (and
						occasionally finishing them). In my free time, I like to spend my free
						time doing <span class="text-secondary">web development</span>,
						learning about infrastructure, and bouldering. I'm currently a co-op
						software developer for
						<span class="text-tertiary">Berlinguette Group</span>, where I'm
						helping to support nuclear fusion research!
					</p>
					<div class="contact">
						<span>Contact me:</span>
						<div class="contact-socials">
							<GitHub />
							<LinkedIn />
							<Email />
						</div>
					</div>
				</main>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="highlights">
			<h2>Here's some highlights of my experience:</h2>
			<div class="highlights-container">
				<HighlightsCard title="Berlinguette Group" date="Jan 2024 - Now">
					<svg
						slot="icon"
						aria-hidden="true"
						xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
						width="24"
						height="24"
						fill="none"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					>
						<path
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-width="2"
							d="M8.737 8.737a21.49 21.49 0 0 1 3.308-2.724m0 0c3.063-2.026 5.99-2.641 7.331-1.3 1.827 1.828.026 6.591-4.023 10.64-4.049 4.049-8.812 5.85-10.64 4.023-1.33-1.33-.736-4.218 1.249-7.253m6.083-6.11c-3.063-2.026-5.99-2.641-7.331-1.3-1.827 1.828-.026 6.591 4.023 10.64m3.308-9.34a21.497 21.497 0 0 1 3.308 2.724m2.775 3.386c1.985 3.035 2.579 5.923 1.248 7.253-1.336 1.337-4.245.732-7.295-1.275M14 12a2 2 0 1 1-4 0 2 2 0 0 1 4 0Z"
						></path>
					</svg>

					At Berlinguette Group, we're doing experimental research into uses of
					electrochemistry to enhance nuclear fusion rates. As a co-op software
					developer, I'm working on our central experiment control interface
					using technologies like React, Python, Docker, Arduino, and MQTT.
				</HighlightsCard>
				<hr>
				<HighlightsCard title="UBC BIOMOD Club" date="May 2023 - Now">
					<svg
						slot="icon"
						aria-hidden="true"
						xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
						width="24"
						height="24"
						fill="none"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					>
						<path
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							stroke-width="2"
							d="M15.041 13.862A4.999 4.999 0 0 1 17 17.831V21M7 3v3.169a5 5 0 0 0 1.891 3.916M17 3v3.169a5 5 0 0 1-2.428 4.288l-5.144 3.086A5 5 0 0 0 7 17.831V21M7 5h10M7.399 8h9.252M8 16h8.652M7 19h10"
						></path>
					</svg>

					Our club competes in the international BIOMOD competition, which is a
					biomolecular design competition. As a co-lead for the website team,
					I'm guiding of a team of 8 to overhaul and modernize our club's
					website. I also helped develop the website for our 2023 competition
					submission, where we placed 5th internationally!
				</HighlightsCard>
				<hr>
				<HighlightsCard title="UBC ARC" date="May 2023 - Dec 2023">
					<svg
						slot="icon"
						aria-hidden="true"
						xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
						width="24"
						height="24"
						fill="none"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					>
						<path
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							stroke-width="2"
							d="m8 9 3 3-3 3m5 0h3M4 19h16a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V6a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v12a1 1 0 0 0 1 1Z"
						></path>
					</svg>

					UBC Advanced Research Computing provides high-performance compute
					capabilities to researchers and students at the university. As a
					datacentre technician intern, I provided support and maintenance for
					over 450 servers consisting of nearly 16,000 CPU cores, 200 GPUs, and
					3 petabytes of storage capacity.
				</HighlightsCard>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page {
		padding: 0 28px;
		@media (min-width: 1024px) {
			padding: 0 92px;
		}
	}

	.bio {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		align-self: stretch;
		gap: 32px;
		padding: 12px 0;

		@media (min-width: 768px) {
			flex-direction: row;
			justify-content: space-between;
			padding: 24px 0;
		}
	}

	.bio-headshot {
		width: 50%;
		/* background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), var(--secondary), var(--tertiary)); */
		/* border: 1px solid black; */
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 2px;
		/* box-shadow: -8px 8px 0 0 black; */
		@media (min-width: 768px) {
			order: 1;
			width: 20%;
			margin-right: 40px;
		}
	}

	.bio-headshot--image {
		border: 1px solid black;
		box-shadow: -8px 8px 0 0 black;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		border-radius: 12px;
	}

	.content {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: start;
		gap: 12px;
		@media (min-width: 768px) {
			flex-basis: 50%;
		}
	}

	.content main {
		line-height: 175%;
		font-size: 18px;

		@media (min-width: 1024px) {
			font-size: 24px;
		}
	}

	.hero_title {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.hero_title--name {
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.contact {
		margin-top: 4px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: row;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 20px;
	}

	.contact-socials {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: row;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 12px;
	}

	.highlights {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 20px;
		padding: 12px 0;
	}

	.highlights-container {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 20px;
		@media (min-width: 1024px) {
			flex-direction: row;
			gap: 36px;
		}
	}

	hr {
		width: 95%;
		border-top: 1px solid black;
		@media (min-width: 1024px) {
			display: none;
		}
	}
</style>
